About 2 weeks ago I made a radio mount that can house both form factors for the Champs radio and the normal competition radio.

cad.onshape.com

Onshape

Sign in to Onshape, the #1 fastest growing CAD system in the world with over 4 million users.

This radio mount also has cable tie holes across the top, and other M5 holes for mounting that can be changed if you want to copy the document. It is designed to be 3D printed with really any filament you choose. You may also want to change your team number.

Happy mounting!
